data.description: Great Space! Great Location! This three bedroom, two bathroom with walkout basement rests on over two acres and includes a screened porch, fenced backyard, private patio, and 24X24 wired shop with attic storage. Large primary suite with gas logs, walk in closet and spacious ensuite with garden tub. Partially finished basement with gas heat and projector/screen could be used as an additional bedroom or flex space. Working, wood burning stove in living area. Newer stainless steel appliances. Roof replaced 2023. Your vision and personal touch is all that is needed to turn this house into a home.
